section.section:
"Eligible low income taxpayer" means an individual, or an individual and the individual's spouse if they file a joint income tax return:
whose federal adjusted gross income as modified under §§ 10-204 through 10-206 of this title does not exceed the applicable poverty income level;
whose earned income as defined under § 32(c)(2) of the Internal Revenue Code does not exceed the applicable poverty income level;
who is not claimed as an exemption on another individual's tax return under § 10-211 of this title; and
for whom the credit allowed under § 10-704(a)(1) of this subtitle is less than the State income tax.
